headline: MEDIA ALERT: Equinix Sets Conference Call for Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year Results
summary: Equinix, Inc. (Nasdaq: EQIX), the world's digital infrastructure company®, today announced that it will hold its quarterly conference call on Wednesday, February 12, 2025, at 5:30 p.m. ET (2:30 p.m. PT). The company will discuss fourth-quarter results for the period ended December 31, 2024, and the full year of 2024.
